rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I got demoted for my part in
letting Iira's cronies escape.

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0002
rows.name: Back to guarding the good old garrison.

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But being caught between my superiors
and subordinates as captain was stressful,
so this is a bit of a relief.

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0004
rows.name:
My pay's taken a huge cut,
but this is probably just
the right level for me.

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Meleph-sama!? Why have
you returned to Torigo!?

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0007
rows.name:
I, the unworthy Pax, shall
devote myself entirely to my
guard duties, as is my station!
